data.text:
Annual Donor List

Lincoln Center gratefully acknowledges the many individuals, foundations, corporations, and government agencies whose generous gifts provide vital support to our commitment to artistic excellence and civic engagement. Listed below are those patrons whose annual gifts are indispensable to the success of our mission. If you would like to join our family of funders, please contact Erin Debold at [email protected] or call (212) 875-5048.
